        "name": "SQA acceptance criteria — MRL 2",
        "description": "Commercial CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1) with documented release validation suite. Version control and change-log records maintained for all user-defined functions. Achieved Gradation 2: documented SQA plan with traceability to solver release notes."
      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1 is a commercially validated solver with published V&V documentation. User-defined hemolysis power-law subroutine is version-controlled in the project repository with unit-test evidence. SQA plan reviewed and approved by quality assurance lead."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/factor/ncv",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
